<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="bg-indigo-600">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
          <span class="block">お祭りの「今」がわかる</span>
          <span class="block text-indigo-200">Yatai Now</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-md mx-auto text-base text-indigo-100 sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl md:max-w-3xl">
          リアルタイムで屋台の位置情報をチェック。<br>
          混雑状況や移動中の屋台も、もう見逃さない。
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 max-w-sm mx-auto sm:max-w-none sm:flex sm:justify-center">
          <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:mx-auto sm:inline-grid sm:grid-cols-1 sm:gap-5">
            <%= link_to map_path, class: "flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-indigo-700 bg-white hover:bg-indigo-50 sm:px-8" do %>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 013 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 011.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0121 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 00-.553-.894L15 7m0 13V7m0 0L9 7" />
              </svg>
              マップを見る
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- How it works -->
  <div class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="lg:text-center">
        <h2 class="text-base text-indigo-600 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">使い方</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl leading-8 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Yatai Nowでできること
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10">
        <dl class="space-y-10 md:space-y-0 md:grid md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-x-8 md:gap-y-10">
          <div class="relative">
            <dt>
              <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-indigo-500 text-white">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">マップを開く</p>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
              「マップを見る」ボタンをタップして、現在開催中のお祭りエリアの地図を表示します。
            </dd>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <dt>
              <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-indigo-500 text-white">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">屋台を探す</p>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
              地図上のアイコンが屋台の現在地です。お目当ての屋台がどこにいるか一目でわかります。
            </dd>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <dt>
              <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-indigo-500 text-white">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">楽しむ！</p>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
              屋台を見つけたら、美味しいお祭りの味を楽しみましょう！
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
